General Assembly House Joint
Resolution No. 30
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1713
Referred to Committee on EXECUTIVE AND LEGISLATIVE
NOMINATIONS
Introduced by:
REP. CONCEPCION, 4th Dist.
SEN. DUFF, 25th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF DELWYN F.
CUMMINGS OF MERIDEN TO BE A MEMBER OF THE BOARD OF
REGENTS FOR HIGHER EDUCATION.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of Delwyn F.
2 Cummings of Meriden to be a member of the Board of Regents for
3 Higher Education, in succession to James F. McCarthy, Jr., to serve a
4 term ending June 30, 2031, or until a successor is appointed and has
5 qualified, whichever is longer, is hereby approved and confirmed.
LCO No. 1713 1 of 1

